      "description": "Fair-condition driver that is usable and presentable, but it clearly shows age and wear throughout. Expect visible cosmetic blemishes, an older-looking interior, and the kind of imperfections and deferred upkeep common in a car at this level. It should appeal most to someone looking for an affordable driver or project they can improve over time, rather than a turn-key showpiece.",
