      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this car could be a great fit for someone who wants affordable wheels, a handy runabout, or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it\u2019s a straightforward option at a sensible price, and I\u2019m happy to answer questions so you know exactly what you\u2019re coming to see. If you\u2019re after value and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this one could be well worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a tough-running powertrain and dependable mechanical fundamentals. Starts, runs, and moves with the kind of straightforward, no-nonsense character that makes it a great option for someone who appreciates usable transportation or a platform to sort and improve over time. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, but the chassis still offers plenty of practical service left for the next owner. If you want an affordable car with real utility and room to add value, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Gets you there. Rough around the edges, priced to sell fast. Cheap entry point for a work car or project.",
